main event: A woman reported seeing an object in the sky that she believed was a Russian lost missile, which fell into the Great South Bay near her beach house in Long Island, New York.
interesting points: The woman reported the sighting to the Duty Officers at the SAC Base in West Hampton, Long Island, but did not hear back.
The woman subsequently reported the sighting to the FBI.
The woman claimed to have recovered a piece of garment from her house, and had moved out of her Long Island house to her town house because she felt she was being watched.
The woman stated that if she did not get any action soon, she was going to take the matter up with Senator Robert Wagner.
The report concluded that this was a Psychological Case.
sighted object: an unidentified object in the sky
